## steward:guard

Scenario        | Invocation                      | Expected                      | ✓/✗
----------------|---------------------------------|-------------------------------|----
cmd-present     | guard bash                      | exits subshell (skip)         | $(t guard:cmd-present)
cmd-absent      | guard nonexistent-cmd           | continues execution           | $(t guard:cmd-absent)
